<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Dashboard de Qualidade</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@600;800;900&family=Inter+Tight:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.1/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0d1015; --panel:#161a23; --panel2:#1c2230; --line:#262d3d;
  --ink:#eaecf2; --muted:#8b93a7; --dim:#5b6478;
  --accent:#ff5b3a; --accent2:#ffd166; --good:#3ddc97; --bad:#ff5b6e; --info:#6cb6ff; --purple:#b07cff;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif;font-size:13.5px}
.app{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh}
header.top{padding:16px 28px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#13171f,#0d1015)}
.brand h1{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:900;font-size:22px;margin:0;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.brand h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--accent)}
.brand .sub{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}
.upload{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.fbtn{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);padding:8px 14px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:12.5px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;transition:.15s}
.fbtn:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.fbtn.ok{border-color:var(--good);color:var(--good)}
.fbtn input{display:none}
.fbtn .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--dim)}
.fbtn.ok .dot{background:var(--good);box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--good)}
.refresh{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);padding:8px 10px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:.15s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:34px;height:34px}
.refresh:hover{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);transform:rotate(90deg)}
.refresh:disabled{opacity:.3;cursor:not-allowed}
nav.tabs{display:flex;padding:0 28px;background:#10141b;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);overflow-x:auto;gap:0}
.tab{padding:14px 20px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;font-size:13px;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;white-space:nowrap;transition:.15s;letter-spacing:.01em}
.tab:hover{color:var(--ink)}
.tab.active{color:var(--ink);border-bottom-color:var(--accent)}
.tab .num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;color:var(--dim);margin-right:8px;font-size:11px}
.tab.active .num{color:var(--accent)}
.filters{padding:12px 28px;background:var(--panel);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:end;flex-wrap:wrap}
.filt{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;min-width:140px}
.filt label{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;font-weight:600}
.filt select,.filt input{background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);padding:7px 10px;border-radius:5px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;outline:none;min-height:34px}
.filt select:focus,.filt input:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.multi-years{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:5px;padding:4px;min-height:34px;align-items:center}
.year-chip{padding:3px 9px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;transition:.15s;user-select:none}
.year-chip:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}
.year-chip.active{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border-color:var(--accent);font-weight:600}
.filt-clear{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);padding:7px 14px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;height:34px}
.filt-clear:hover{color:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
main{padding:24px 28px;flex:1}
.empty{text-align:center;padding:80px 20px;color:var(--muted);border:2px dashed var(--line);border-radius:12px;margin:40px}
.empty h2{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);font-size:28px;margin:0 0 10px}
.empty code{background:var(--panel);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;color:var(--accent2);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px}
.page{display:none}
.page.active{display:block;animation:fade .25s ease}
@keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(4px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.kpis{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-bottom:20px}
.kpi{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 18px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.kpi::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:3px;background:var(--accent)}
.kpi.good::before{background:var(--good)}.kpi.bad::before{background:var(--bad)}.kpi.info::before{background:var(--info)}.kpi.warn::before{background:var(--accent2)}
.kpi .lbl{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px}
.kpi .val{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:800;font-size:30px;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05}
.kpi .sub{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:4px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.grid{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px}
.grid-2{grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(420px,1fr))}
.grid-3{grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr))}
.card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.card.featured{border-color:var(--accent);border-width:1.5px;box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(255,91,58,.15)}
.card h3{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 4px;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.card .desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px}
.card.tall{min-height:360px}
.card .canvas-wrap{position:relative;flex:1;min-height:260px}
.card.tall .canvas-wrap{min-height:300px}
table.data{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12.5px}
table.data th,table.data td{text-align:left;padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
table.data th{color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--panel);z-index:1}
table.data td.num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;text-align:right}
table.data tr:hover td{background:var(--panel2)}
.scroll-y{max-height:480px;overflow-y:auto}
.bar-cell{position:relative;padding:0!important}
.bar-cell .bar{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent),transparent);opacity:.18}
.bar-cell .lbl{position:relative;padding:8px 10px;display:block}
.badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.badge.good{background:rgba(61,220,151,.15);color:var(--good)}
.badge.bad{background:rgba(255,91,110,.15);color:var(--bad)}
.status{font-size:11px;color:var(--dim);padding:10px 28px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;gap:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.status b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
.loading{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(13,16,21,.85);display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:100;backdrop-filter:blur(4px)}
.loading.show{display:flex}
.loading .box{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);padding:24px 32px;border-radius:10px;text-align:center}
.spinner{width:36px;height:36px;border:3px solid var(--line);border-top-color:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:spin 1s linear infinite;margin:0 auto 12px}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--good);color:var(--good);padding:12px 20px;border-radius:8px;z-index:200;animation:slideIn .3s;font-weight:500}
.toast.err{border-color:var(--bad);color:var(--bad)}
@keyframes slideIn{from{transform:translateY(20px);opacity:0}to{transform:none;opacity:1}}
/* AJUSTES */
.settings-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:14px}
.settings-card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:20px}
.settings-card h3{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;margin:0 0 6px}
.settings-card .desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px}
.form-row{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.form-row label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);min-width:120px}
.form-row input,.form-row select{background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);padding:7px 10px;border-radius:5px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;outline:none;flex:1;min-width:100px}
.form-row input:focus,.form-row select:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.btn{background:var(--accent);border:none;color:#fff;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;transition:.15s}
.btn:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}
.btn.ghost{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted)}
.btn.ghost:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.btn.good{background:var(--good);color:#0d1015}
.btn.bad{background:var(--bad)}
.config-info{background:var(--panel2);border-left:3px solid var(--info);padding:12px 14px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.config-info b{color:var(--ink)}
.editable-list{max-height:340px;overflow-y:auto;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px}
.editable-list .row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr 1.2fr auto;gap:8px;padding:6px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);align-items:center;font-size:12px}
.editable-list .row:last-child{border-bottom:0}
.editable-list .row:hover{background:var(--panel2)}
.editable-list input{background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;color:var(--ink);padding:4px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;width:100%}
.editable-list input:hover{border-color:var(--line)}
.editable-list input:focus{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--panel2);outline:none}
.editable-list code{color:var(--muted);font-size:11.5px}
.del-btn{background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--dim);cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px}
.del-btn:hover{color:var(--bad)}
.search-box{background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink);padding:8px 12px;border-radius:5px;font-family:inherit;font-size:13px;width:100%;margin-bottom:10px;outline:none}
.search-box:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
@media(max-width:760px){.grid-2,.grid-3{grid-template-columns:1fr}header.top{padding:14px}main{padding:16px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">
<header class="top">
  <div class="brand"><h1>Quality<em>·</em>Dash</h1><div class="sub">Indicadores de Defeitos · 2017 — Abr/2026</div></div>
  <div class="upload">
    <label class="fbtn" id="btnDef"><span class="dot"></span><span id="lblDef">Carregar Defeitos</span><input type="file" id="fileDef" accept=".xlsx,.xls"></label>
    <button class="refresh" id="rfDef" title="Recarregar arquivo de defeitos" disabled>↻</button>
    <label class="fbtn" id="btnProd"><span class="dot"></span><span id="lblProd">Carregar Produção</span><input type="file" id="fileProd" accept=".xlsx,.xls"></label>
    <button class="refresh" id="rfProd" title="Recarregar arquivo de produção" disabled>↻</button>
  </div>
</header>
<nav class="tabs" id="tabs">
  <div class="tab active" data-page="overview"><span class="num">01</span>Visão Geral</div>
  <div class="tab" data-page="defects"><span class="num">02</span>Defeitos</div>
  <div class="tab" data-page="clients"><span class="num">03</span>Clientes</div>
  <div class="tab" data-page="consultants"><span class="num">04</span>Consultores</div>
  <div class="tab" data-page="types"><span class="num">05</span>Tipos &amp; Locais</div>
  <div class="tab" data-page="trends"><span class="num">06</span>Tendências</div>
  <div class="tab" data-page="settings" style="margin-left:auto"><span class="num">⚙</span>Ajustes</div>
</nav>
<div class="filters" id="filters" style="display:none">
  <div class="filt" style="min-width:260px"><label>Anos (múltipla seleção)</label><div class="multi-years" id="fAnos"></div></div>
  <div class="filt"><label>Mês</label><select id="fMes"><option value="">Todos</option></select></div>
  <div class="filt"><label>Material</label><select id="fMat"><option value="">Todos</option></select></div>
  <div class="filt"><label>Consultor</label><select id="fCons"><option value="">Todos</option></select></div>
  <div class="filt" style="min-width:220px"><label>Cliente</label><select id="fCli"><option value="">Todos</option></select></div>
  <button class="filt-clear" id="btnClear">Limpar filtros</button>
</div>
<main id="main">
  <div class="empty" id="empty">
    <h2>Carregue os dois arquivos para começar</h2>
    <p>Arquivos esperados: <code>Defeitos</code> e <code>Produção</code> (.xlsx)</p>
    <p style="margin-top:18px">Os dados ficam <b>somente no seu navegador</b> — nada é enviado a servidores.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:14px;font-size:12px">Dica: use a aba <b>⚙ Ajustes</b> para importar <code>config.json</code> da pasta compartilhada.</p>
  </div>
  <section class="page" id="page-overview"></section>
  <section class="page" id="page-defects"></section>
  <section class="page" id="page-clients"></section>
  <section class="page" id="page-consultants"></section>
  <section class="page" id="page-types"></section>
  <section class="page" id="page-trends"></section>
  <section class="page" id="page-settings"></section>
</main>
<div class="status" id="status"></div>
</div>
<div class="loading" id="loading"><div class="box"><div class="spinner"></div><div id="loadMsg">Processando…</div></div></div>

